Return a specific domain from a sdtm object

Source: R/sdtm_class.R
domain.Rd

Return a specific domain from a sdtm object

Usage

domain(obj, name)

Arguments

obj

The sdtm object.

name

The domain to return.

Value

The specified domain as data.frame

Examples

head(domain(examplinib_fe, "dm"))
